{"tid":1470278,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想同813機場前線講聲多謝","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:07:24.000Z","uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69ed2b6b092ef39521644dcce5f39f00a4fcfaa3","tid":1470278,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:44:56.000Z","msg":"利申：機場集會差唔多去哂，就係琴日冇去。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚開始就已經大量冷氣軍師出黎屌前線，個個都話「我好嬲啊，咁同xxx有咩分別」。我屌番你啦，有本事你就入機場拉住大家做勸交撚。<br />\n<br />\n個個都講到自己好有道德，係聖人咁。你唔係現場，你確定你清楚當時既情況？811都可以有警察扮示威者，我合理懷疑琴日在場一定都有警察起哄，令現場氣氛更繃緊。<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n所以，<br />\n所以，<br />\n我好想多謝琴日既手足，我知你們備受壓力。雖然我地的確有改善既地方，但人地設左個咁大既局畀我地，我地手足依然好有智慧去應對。希望你唔好一起身碌fb ig, 就被大量責罵post 影響心情。我想講你地真係好叻，尤其琴晚飛身救女途人既巴打們，你地真係型到出汁，完全體現到團隊精神。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後要繼續進步，全香港人都要一齊進步。阿爺見呢招打唔殘我地，一定會再出陰招，我們堅持住三大底線，四大原則就可以。要比之前更團結，不可忘記五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n「我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。」<br />\n<br />\n- 梁天琦 《梁天琦致香港人的信》2019.7.29<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n香港人日程：<br />\n816 全民提款日<br />\n818 全民大遊行"},{"pid":"4b907de6be8934b302d489d944583c349fe77dec","tid":1470278,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:46:59.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<br />\n做錯事不道歉，是違反道德的啊。這個當然，但我們不是在小學課室，由班長和班主任裁判，我們是在戰場上，警察、法官、電視台、報紙、觀眾都是中共的人。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你道歉，對方就有材料展開政治謠言宣傳，而且要求你再為其他你無做過的事道歉（例如毆打北京記者），之後你拒絕，他們就向你開火射擊。</span></span>做錯了事就馬上走，不是道歉！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">普選勝利了，在民選元首認為安全的情況</span></span>，才為以往的錯失道歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道歉也是元首來做，不是民眾來做</span></span>，賠償也是用政府的錢，不是民間眾籌。"},{"pid":"e8817e89378281ebf8b5fd12fd07ca1f3292d3a9","tid":1470278,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"【重要通知】抗爭不割蓆手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請參閱"},{"pid":"d3bbc2c334a5a583b511ad9296688eaf1507f4d1","tid":1470278,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"三不主張 四大底線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466149</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b031a6c4413ccf56fc203bd55c92310a7b922a3","tid":1470278,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:04:26.000Z","msg":"台灣旅客 今日機場經歷 大家睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"514e483695b610799de4f3da3f0b26f8b69ffe92","tid":1470278,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"[818遊行]我哋而家應該要推爆818遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e5b4ac0eb676034a7cf814743ac168d5a037f7ed","tid":1470278,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:07:24.000Z","msg":"唔準再互屌，只準互呵！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}